OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776885106
OL,3,CTrial of football fan accused of
OL,4,Cracially abusing Antoine Semenyo
OL,5,Cadjourned
OL,7,FThe case of a Liverpool FC supporter
OL,8,Faccused of racially abusing footballer
OL,9,FAntoine Semenyo has been adjourned
OL,10,Fafter questions were raised about
OL,11,Fwhether he is fit to stand trial.
OL,13,FMark Mogan, 47, was due to stand trial
OL,14,Fat Liverpool Magistrates' Court on 22
OL,15,FApril accused of racially aggravated
OL,16,Fbehaviour during a match at Anfield in
OL,17,FAugust 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
