PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776885106
OL,3,CTrial of football fan accused of
OL,4,Cracially abusing Antoine Semenyo
OL,5,Cadjourned
OL,7,FOlivia Belle, defending, said Mogan,
OL,8,Fwho has cerebral palsy and uses a
OL,9,Fwheelchair, had been assessed by a
OL,10,Fpsychiatric expert who found he was
OL,11,Funfit to plead or stand trial.
OL,13,FShe said he had a "highly complex
OL,14,Fpresentation" and a history of
OL,15,Flanguage and communication
OL,16,Fdifficulties.
OL,26,@uD@SOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
