OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776885106
OL,3,CTrial of football fan accused of
OL,4,Cracially abusing Antoine Semenyo
OL,5,Cadjourned
OL,7,FSemenyo had been due to give evidence
OL,8,Fin the one-day trial, but the court
OL,9,Fheard witnesses had been told not to
OL,10,Fattend when it became clear the case
OL,11,Fwould not go ahead.
OL,13,FDistrict Judge James Hatton adjourned
OL,14,Fthe case to September to allow the
OL,15,Fprosecution to obtain their own
OL,16,Fpsychiatric report.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
