FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776885106
OL,3,CTrial of football fan accused of
OL,4,Cracially abusing Antoine Semenyo
OL,5,Cadjourned
OL,7,FMogan, of Templehill Close, Dovecot,
OL,8,Fwas given bail with conditions
OL,9,Fincluding that he must not contact
OL,10,FSemenyo, attend any regulated football
OL,11,Fmatches, or go within one mile of
OL,12,FPremier and Football League grounds
OL,13,Faround the time of games.
OL,15,FThe defendant, who attended court with
OL,16,Fhis father, is accused of directing
OL,17,Fabuse at the 26-year-old player at the
OL,18,FPremier League Liverpool v Bournemouth
OL,19,Ffixture on 15 August.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
