OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776885106
OL,3,CTrial of football fan accused of
OL,4,Cracially abusing Antoine Semenyo
OL,5,Cadjourned
OL,7,FMatch referee Anthony Taylor stopped
OL,8,Fplay in the 29th minute after Semenyo,
OL,9,Fthen a Bournemouth player, reported
OL,10,Fthe abuse and a man was ejected from
OL,11,Fthe stadium.
OL,13,FThe footballer, who has since signed
OL,14,Ffor Manchester City, went on to score
OL,15,Ftwice in the second half to help bring
OL,16,FBournemouth back from two goals down
OL,17,Fat Anfield before Liverpool went on to
OL,18,Feventually win 4-2.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
